    "Body": " We at Mothership are looking for a content marketer / copywriter who can drive our content strategy and of course create valuable content for our community. You'll be working to create content that we can share with our audiences, use in our advertisement material, on our website, etc and drive the content strategy and efforts. So if you obsess about the use of language, making difficult concepts easy to understand, and are able to spin even the worst news in a positive manner, then we want you to join the team! RESPONSIBILITY - Help us identify content opportunities that would be interesting to our audience with business goals in mind - Write & edit blog posts, emails and social media messages - Create content marketing strategies to improve conversions throughout the customer journey - Develop user persona's based on our target audiences - Develop the editorial calendar and ensure deadlines are met - Optimize content for search engines (SEO) - Work together with the design team to get visuals for content - Work with the various teams internally to gather information and knowledge we can add to our content REQUIREMENTS - Relevant experience in content marketing for at least 3 years - Native english speaker or at least 10 years of work experience in English - Experience & knowledge on structuring content for SEO - Have a basic knowledge of cryptocurrencies and blockchain technology - Willing to learn technical aspects of the product - Passion for creating valuable content - No degree requirements, just show us you can do the job! WHAT WE CAN OFFER We know it sounds clich????????????, but we would definitely classify Mothership as a fast-growing startup with open-minded individuals that are all contributing to our daily growth. If you enjoy working with talented individuals from all sorts of backgrounds, whether that's corporate environments or well-known startups, and enjoy a good bit of fun every so often, then we are certain you'll fit right in. - A competitive salary. Let's talk numbers during the interview! - Visa sponsorship and relocation package or be able to work remotely. - All the books you can read. For free. - Whatever equipment you need to do your job. - Smart and motivated team from all over the world in a well-funded startup. LOCATION Mothership is based in Tallinn, Estonia. It's a quiet and beautiful city with an excellent infrastructure. We offer a relocation package and will help you get a visa. But if you love it where you are, consider remote employees are first-class citizens in our company; we embrace the remote development culture. Skills content marketing, editing, copywriting Compensation Let's discuss numbers during the interview Applications for this job are currently closed. ", 
